data.description: Affordable move in ready 3 bedroom 2.5 bath single family home with fenced back yard and screened in porch. Welcome to 3610 Mactavish Ave. This single family home is ready for you to move in and just add your personal touch! The main level offers open concept living with a spacious living room adjacent to the upgraded eat in kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite countertop island and room for dining table. Relax on the screened in porch with views of the fenced in yard. The upper level has two spacious bedroom with a full updated bathroom and a finished lower level with an additional bedroom or flex space. There is a full update bathroom at the lower level for added convenience and a private walk up entry from the lower level to the back yard.  The laundry and utility room complete the lower level. The fenced rear yard offers extra space for entertaining and gardening. At this price it won't last. Schedule your private showing now.
